<Content>A Great Hotel Great Location Stayed at BALMORAL last week end Service could not be faulted Room was excellent, clean sheets and Towels everyday. Well done Stella (our elusive chambermaid).Right in the middle of the exclusive financal area of Barcelona - Really good shops around the vacinity of the hotelLocated only a few mins walk from the Metro, where the trains are very frequent.and clean.Don't forget to buy the Very cheap T10 ticket which almost lasted for the whole week end - this is valid for all transport .Barcelona is not cheap so don't think it is, especially around the Ramblas where meals are extortionately priced and have a 7% service charge added on. Tip if you wish???All in all Barcelona is a wonderful city the people were friendly and the sights awsome - plenty going on even a Mexican concert in the Gothic square off the Ramblas dancing and mexican bands- Wonderful! 
