<Content>Great hotel in a good location We stayed in this hotel for 5 nights. The location is near the diagnoal metro stop and buses 16, 17, 22, 24 and 28. It was very central near Casa Mila and other Gaudi sites. It is near the P. de Gracia as well. It was close enough (about a 10 minute bus ride) to Plaza de Catalynua and the Ramblas.. The hotel staff was excellent. Maria helped us plan our days, called the Renfe and other restaurants to find opening times as our spanish was limited. The rooms were clean  very nice.The management even accomodated a change in our stay once we had arrived - they were superb!Would definitely recommend - I booked this hotel through bancotel and paid 50 euros per night. 
